msgid "What Are Rock Cannons?"
msgstr "Beth Yw Canonau Cerrig?"

msgid "Discover rare geological and historical formations across the region. Learn their stories, plan visits, and help protect them for future explorers."
msgstr "Darganfyddwch ffurfiadau daearegol a hanesyddol prin ar draws y rhanbarth. Dysgwch eu straeon, cynlluniwch ymweliadau, a helpwch i'w gwarchod ar gyfer archwilwyr y dyfodol."

